⸻

Each Pantheon entity becomes:

🔍 Hound
	•	triggers anomaly events
	•	flags suspicious data

⸻

🧠 Mirror
	•	generates insight drops
	•	reveals meaning

⸻

🕸️ Spider
	•	connects quests
	•	creates narrative threads

⸻

